HEADWORD: Vaticination
<hw>Va*tic`i*na"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>vaticinatio</ets>.]</ety> <def>Prediction; prophecy.</def>⟦br⟧
